\v 1 Xi³ coan³nchaon³ coan³jnqui³-ni³, ja³ˀa³sˀen³-nca¹ni³ ˀnte³ jña³ nca³ Capernaum ˀmi², ya⁴ tsa³ˀya³-le⁴ nca³ ti¹jna³ˀya³ ni³ˀya³.
