\v 17 Cˀia⁴ nca³ Jesús qui³nčhˀoe¹ je²-vi⁴, qui³tso²-le⁴: Je² cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ nta³, a³li² chji⁴ne⁴xqui³-jin² ma³chjen¹-le⁴, to⁴je² xi³ tjio¹mˀen³ xi³ ma³chjen¹-le⁴ chji⁴ne⁴xqui³. A³li²coi³ je²ˀe⁴ nca³ an³ nca³ coi³nchja²³-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ tjin¹-le⁴ cjoa⁴qui²xi⁴, to⁴je² cho⁴ta⁴je¹ xi³ coi³nchja²³-le⁴.
\s1 Xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ cjoa⁴vi³jna³nchjan³
