\v 26 Jesús cˀoa⁴qui³tso²: Cˀoa⁴-sˀin² ma³nco¹son² je² cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³-le⁴ Ni³na¹, jo³-ni³ tsa² jnco³ cho⁴ta⁴ xi³ vˀe¹tsao³ na⁴xin⁴-le⁴ tso³jmi²ntje² ja⁴jin³ na³nqui³.
\v 27 Va³jna³fe² nca³ ni⁴tjen⁴, vi³so¹tjen⁴ nca³ ni⁴čhjin³. Je² na⁴xin⁴ ma³ntje², ma³jcha¹, to⁴nca³ li²coi³ ve³ cho⁴ta⁴-ve⁴ jo³-sˀin² ma³-ni³.
\v 28 To⁴ya⁴ ma³ntje² jin³na³nqui³ nca³ to⁴je². Ti¹tjon² vi³tjo³ je⁴ˀe⁴, cˀia⁴ ma³ ncho⁴tin⁴, ja⁴scan³ ma³ ni⁴jin⁴.
\v 29 Cˀia⁴ nca³ je³coan³jcha¹ ni⁴jin⁴, nti⁴ton⁴ vi³cha²-ni³ qui⁴cha⁴, nca³ je³ji³cho² ni⁴čhjin³-le⁴ nca³ sˀe⁴xco¹.
\s1 Xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ na⁴xin⁴-le⁴ mostaza
