\v 34 To⁴cao⁴ en¹ xi³ cjoa⁴xco¹son² tsa³cja²cao⁴, to⁴nca³ cˀia⁴ nca³ ti¹jna³cao⁴ tˀa³xin² cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴, qui³tso²ya³nta³-le⁴ nca³yi³je³.
