\v 35 Ti⁴coi³-ni³ ni⁴čhjin³-ve⁴ nca³ coan³xon², cˀoa⁴qui³tso²-le⁴: Coi⁴tja¹ xi³ncoa³tˀa³ nta¹chi³con³.
