\v 18 Jesús ja³ˀa³sˀen³ ya⁴ chi³tso³. Je² xi³ nai⁴² xi³ nta³jin³ qui³si³jti³-le⁴ tsa³cˀe¹tsˀoa³-le⁴ Jesús nca³ ca²ta³vˀe²jna³tˀa³ntsjai²-le⁴.
\v 19 To⁴nca³ Jesús li²coi³ qui³tsjoa³ˀnte²-le⁴, qui³tso²-le⁴: Tˀin³ ni³ˀya³-li⁴, tˀin³chon³-lai⁴ xi²nqui⁴, tˀe²-lai⁴ na⁴jmi¹ jo³ nca³ tjin¹ cjoa⁴nta³ xi³ ca²sˀin¹ xi³ tˀa³tsi⁴ je² Nai³-na¹, jo³-sˀin² nca³ ca²ma³ma⁴que³-li².
\v 20 Qui³ cho⁴ta⁴-ve⁴, tsa³cˀe¹tsˀia⁴cao⁴ nca³ qui³si³nca³son² en¹ ya⁴ ˀnte³ Decápolis, jo³ nca³ tjin¹ cjoa⁴xcon¹ xi³ qui³sˀin³ Jesús xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴. Nca³tsˀi³ cho⁴ta⁴ jo³ coan³xcon¹-le⁴.
\s1 Jairo tsa³cˀe¹tsˀoa³ xi³ tˀa³tsˀe⁴ tso²ti³-le⁴
