\v 45 Jesús tsa³cˀe¹ne² nti⁴ton⁴-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴-le⁴ nca³ ja³ˀa³sˀen³ chi³tso³-ve⁴, nca³ qui³ ti¹tjon²-le⁴ sa³ˀnta³ na⁴xi⁴na³nta¹ Betsaida ya⁴ xi³ncoa³-ni³. Tjen⁴ nca³ tjio¹fi² nca³ je², ti⁴je²-ni³ Jesús tsa³cˀe¹ne²-le⁴ cho⁴ta⁴ncjin² nca³ ca²ta³fi² nca³tsˀi³.
