\v 42 To⁴ˀya³-ni³ve⁴ xi³ si⁴²ca³jnqui³ je¹ jnco³ ˀnti¹ xi³ ma³cjain¹-le⁴ tˀa³tsˀan⁴, cjai¹-la² nca³ nta³-le⁴ tsa² jnco³ la⁴jao⁴ xi³ tsˀe⁴ molino sˀe⁴tˀa³nˀion¹nqui³ ya¹sin³, cˀoa⁴ si⁴cˀa³tjen⁴jin³ nta¹chi³con³ cho⁴ta⁴ xo⁴ cji³-ve⁴.
\v 43 Tsa² ntsai⁴ si¹cji³tson¹-li², to⁴sa³ ti⁴cha³tˀai³. Nqui²sa⁴ nta³ tsa² coi⁴jna³choin³ nca³ co³to³ ntsja³ ti³soi³, cao⁴-ni³ tsa² to⁴jo³ jao² ma³ ntsai⁴, cˀoa⁴ nca³ cha⁴ni²jin³-li² ya⁴ infierno, ya⁴jin³ lˀi¹ xi³ tsi² coan⁴ coi⁴tsˀao³,
