\v 37 Jacobo cao⁴ Juan qui³tso²-le⁴: Cˀia⁴ nca³ sˀe⁴-li² cjoa⁴te¹xo³ma³ cao⁴ cjoa⁴je³ya³-li⁴, tˀai²ˀnte³-na³jin⁴ nca³ coi⁴yo³tˀa³-lai²⁴jin⁴, jnco³ nca³qui²xi⁴-li⁴ xi³jnco³ nca³scon¹-li⁴.
