\v 22 Cˀia⁴ nca³ tjio¹cjen², Jesús qui³scoe¹ nio⁴xti²la⁴, qui³si³chi³con³tˀain³, qui³si³xcoa⁴, qui³tsjoa³-le⁴, qui³tso²: Chjoao¹³, je²-vi⁴ yao³-na⁴ ni¹.
