\v 33 Qui³cao⁴ Pedro, Jacobo, cao⁴ Juan. Jesús tsa³cˀe¹tsˀia⁴ nca³ ja³tse³xcon¹, cˀoa⁴ nˀion¹ qui³si³cjao¹jin³.
